workflowDTO Data Type

Contains the information about a workflow

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
content workflowContentDTO element 0/1 The content from within the Workflow Engine (only used for export)
creator_id objectHandle element 0/1 The user that created the workflow
description string element 0/1 The textual description of the workflow
export_key string element 0/1 This field is used to identify the object during import
last_modified_by objectHandle element 0/1 The user the workflow was last modified by
last_modified_time dateTime element 0/1 The date the workflow was last modified
name string element 0/1 The display name of the workflow
object_type objectHandle element 0/1 The object type of the workflow. e.g. Incident, Task, etc.
programmatic_name string element 0/1 The programmatic name of the workflow.
uuid string element 0/1 This field is used to identify the object during import
workflow_id int element 0/1 The internal ID of the workflow

Example

<workflowDTO>
  <workflow_id>...</workflow_id>
  <name>...</name>
  <programmatic_name>...</programmatic_name>
  <object_type>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
  </object_type>
  <description>...</description>
  <creator_id>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
  </creator_id>
  <last_modified_by>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
  </last_modified_by>
  <last_modified_time>...</last_modified_time>
  <export_key>...</export_key>
  <uuid>...</uuid>
  <content>
    <workflow_id>
      <id>...</id>
      <name>...</name>
    </workflow_id>
    <xml>...</xml>
    <version>...</version>
  </content>
</workflowDTO>
